        <content1 datatype="string" friendlyname="Heading">Welcome</content1>
        <content2 datatype="text" friendlyname="Content"><p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="color: #000000;">We are always pleased to hear from people considering working for us. Our basic requirements are that you must have an adequate level of physical fitness, appropriate professional qualifications and sufficient practical experience for any particular vacancy. You will need to live close enough to work on any site in the greater Bristol area.</span><span style="color: #000000;">&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #000000;">Our normal hours of work are 0800 to 1630 hrs, Monday to Friday. From time to time work outside these hours may be required.</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;"><span style="color: #000000;">Reliability and punctuality are essential requirements.</span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></content2>
